body:
@ambatigan, thanks for letting me know that you are having this issue too. I just noticed that this started happening not so long ago. Yes, I need to upgrade the version of IPFS. It has been on my todo list as the version (0.4.5) is quite a few months old now. 
In this simple test network, I am using 4 Tendermint validators hosted in Google Engine Cluster, plus one IPFS node. Your node needs to register with this IPFS cloud node in order for it to be discoverable through the IPFS DHT Routing logic.
Let me do further investigations to track down the root cause. I'm also sure there is a better way of configuring the swarm.
